<p>[:en] # Wizard of Gems<br>
In Wizard of Gems all twenty bet lines are active on every spin. Winning symbols disappear as if by magic and replacements cascade down to replace them. If this creates any new winning combinations the process repeats itself. This process continues until no winning combination appears.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>On any given round after the first any wins gets multiplied. This game has one wild symbol (the Spell Book) and one free spin scatter symbol (the Star). As we mentioned earlier multiple wins gains a multiplier. To start off the multiplier is one but it increases to two on the second win and to three on the third. After that any wins multiplies by five.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>When three scatter symbols appears on the board ten free spins activates. While these are active at least one and as many as nine wild symbols are active on every spin. If three additional stars appears while in free spin mode another ten freespins are added. However there is a maximum of five times this can happen in a single spin. So the absolute maximum number of free spins wins gives out is fifty (5x10) on a single spin.</p>
